      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. While it runs and drives, it will likely need some mechanical attention soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension refresh, to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s an honest car that reflects its mileage and history.",
