    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been absolutely babied and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or smudge anywhere\u2014it\u2019s honestly in pristine shape and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take a look and fall in love!",
