    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a mechanically superlative example of Porsche\u2019s naturally aspirated flat-six heritage. The 3.6L M96 powerplant delivers a linear torque curve via VarioCam Plus, mated to a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This unit features a documented LN Engineering IMS retrofit and recent bore-scoping to ensure total cylinder wall integrity. The suspension architecture has been enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers, providing surgical turn-in and optimized damping for high-speed stability. Finished in concours-level Arctic Silver, the paint depth remains consistent with factory specifications, showing zero oxidative wear or road rash. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist demanding mechanical perfection.",
